{"key": "{\"messages\": [{\"content\": [{\"text\": \"Warmup\", \"type\": \"text\"}], \"role\": \"user\"}], \"model\": \"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\", \"stop\": null, \"temperature\": 1.0, \"top_k\": null, \"top_p\": null}", "value": {"model": "claude-haiku-4-5-20251001", "id": "msg_018qKQr56wVnxbdUGSR1b1De", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Hello! I'm Claude Code, your file search specialist. I'm ready to help you navigate and explore your codebase.\n\nI can assist you with:\n- **Finding files** using glob patterns\n- **Searching code** with regex patterns\n- **Reading file contents** for analysis\n- **File operations** like listing and exploring directories\n\nYour repository is currently on `branch_1` and appears to be in a clean state. I can see you have recent commits including \"Stuff\", \"app.py commit\", \"add some cool data\", and an initial commit.\n\nWhat would you like me to search for or explore in your codebase?"}], "stop_reason": "end_turn", "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 495, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0, "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 0, "ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0}, "output_tokens": 141, "service_tier": "standard"}}}
