{"key": "{\"messages\": [{\"content\": \"Hello, this is a test message!\", \"role\": \"user\"}, {\"content\": [{\"text\": \"Hello! I'm Sculptor, an AI coding agent powered by Claude Code. I'm here to help you with coding tasks like:\\n\\n- Writing new code\\n- Fixing bugs\\n- Refactoring\\n- Answering questions about your codebase\\n- Running tests and builds\\n- And much more!\\n\\nBefore I can help you effectively, let me check what's in your repository:\", \"type\": \"text\"}, {\"id\": \"toolu_01YAHaxTrnu645mYn93rznEw\", \"input\": {\"command\": \"pwd\", \"description\": \"Check current working directory\"}, \"name\": \"Bash\", \"type\": \"tool_use\"}, {\"id\": \"toolu_01XuCVbXArFejWvFufaCqQcL\", \"input\": {\"command\": \"ls -la\", \"description\": \"List all files in repository\"}, \"name\": \"Bash\", \"type\": \"tool_use\"}], \"role\": \"assistant\"}], \"model\": \"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\", \"stop\": null, \"temperature\": 1.0, \"top_k\": null, \"top_p\": null}", "value": {"model": "claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929", "id": "msg_01LApJfeFa5nhyhi1Me2AVFr", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Great! I can see you have a repository with:\n- A `src/` directory (likely containing your source code)\n- A `data/` directory\n- A README.md file\n- A stuff.txt file\n- Git is initialized on branch `branch_1`\n\nWhat would you like me to help you with today? I can explore your codebase, write new features, fix bugs, or answer questions about your code."}], "stop_reason": "end_turn", "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 8, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 3967, "cache_read_input_tokens": 11638, "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 3967, "ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0}, "output_tokens": 97, "service_tier": "standard"}}}
